Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpIf Kamala is reelected, one of her very first acts will be to MASSIVELY raise taxes on American Families. Kamala Harris is the TAX QUEEN.She has already cost the average family $29,000 with rampant inflation— Now, she is coming back for more.
